-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_43&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from AOL member vbkorik27 previously at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a>.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/04/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-25\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 25</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.se/2014/03/re-read-arya-viii-dark-heart.html\">Re-read Arya VIII: Dark Heart</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.se/2014/03/re-read-arya-viii-dark-heart-contd.html\">Re-read Arya VIII: Dark Heart (Cont'd)</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403095346\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.243 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1096/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9082/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1841/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.29 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  212.113     